title: Chateau De Ville Hutch & Buffet
description:
The Chateau De Ville hutch and buffet offers you plenty of space for all your fine dining accessories from napkin rings to serving platters. The top cabinet is accessed via two tall, arched doors and is outfitted with clear glass panels on the front and sides that allow you to clearly see the contents. Two single-door cabinets are built into the base of the unit, complemented by six pull-out drawers. The frame is built from solid hardwood with molded borders and carved side pillars. A floral medallion crowns the double-arched top.
